text: Jackson Rondinelli (born 20 May 1994) is a Brazilian diver. He competed in the men's synchronized ten metre platform event at the 2016 Summer Olympics. He started diving at the age of 15 in São Paulo, and had his first competition as a national open in 2010. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian male divers Category:Olympic divers of Brazil Category:Divers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Divers at the 2015 Pan American Games
